    {
        "content": "<p>I'm trying to use the indexing functions on Lists/Arrays, but I keep getting stuck on how to make the proofs. For instance, I can do this:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">length</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>But what about something like this?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">def</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xids</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">ids</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">ids</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">foldl</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">fun</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">=&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">???</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>And how about generating the ids?</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">opaque</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">get_some_ids</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">-&gt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span>\n<span class=\"kn\">axiom</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ids_valid</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">List</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Nat</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∀</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">get_some_ids</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">id</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">&lt;</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">xs</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">length</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I can't seem to connect them.</p>",
